{"tid":2153620,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人屋企人仲衰過死藍屍","createTime":"2020-08-12T15:41:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-12T20:45:43.000Z","uid":215219,"like":2,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"9949c954f81f931ac3827edff49717a0fe6fdeec","tid":2153620,"uid":215219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T15:41:48.000Z","msg":"有冇人屋企人日日喺Facebook share文宣，警暴嘅片<br />\n仲開post一齊鬧班警犬，但係就成日食元氣，買美心閪餅。<br />\n<br />\n之前就話買美心係用之前啲餅卡，咁我咪當費事曬咗啲卡。<br />\n但係元氣係佢真金白銀買。仲要話好好食，外賣仲有折，真係痴鳩線。<br />\n<br />\n我話佢哋，佢哋仲要個10歲細佬跟住佢癲，<br />\n同我講話聽日會去買埋吉野家。<br />\n<br />\n有時寧願屋企人係真藍屍好過假黃絲。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9beae5356ca186ed08efc2372eeeef7b6c2e3ac","tid":2153620,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T15:42:42.000Z","msg":"佢地藍扮黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a92d1aade609e12cea0d56559f0615dcf2368f5a","tid":2153620,"uid":215219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f9beae5356ca186ed08efc2372eeeef7b6c2e3ac","tid":2153620,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T15:42:42.000Z","msg":"佢地藍扮黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T15:51:05.000Z","msg":"好撚辛苦啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47c65c6cc7fe51e395619412cf0afc94b2161296","tid":2153620,"uid":362816,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T15:53:57.000Z","msg":"我老母都係咁，偽黃"},{"pid":"44e8bcb7e0e101e8ea566ce82a56290633111c5d","tid":2153620,"uid":116343,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T19:16:03.000Z","msg":"藍絲有好多種 你屋企人可以話係淺藍 想食曬兩家茶禮⋯<br />\n我成屋都又紅又藍 日日覺得共產黨俾到飽飯你食就夠 仲話好多人想買兇殺咗trump trump<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你就知道 你既處境低處未算低<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f08babc84b17f96b079947b81c5027874